<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>Nolt<ex>en</ex></expan></del> von <expan cert="medium">Seck<ex>endorf</ex></expan> . 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Nolt <expan>gena<ex>n</ex>t</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_22_r2l2">cʒu Tetelſaw geſeſſen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
