<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hiltpolt<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan cert="medium">Seck<ex>endorf</ex></expan>, czu Tetelsaw gesessen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Hiltpolt, uns hat
                                <expan>fürgel<ex>egt</ex></expan> Lucz
                            <expan>Steinling<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz im der Hans Lucz von Michelbach,
                        sein armman, geklagt hab, daz er vor dem Hansen Smyde und seinen sünen von
                        Herczogenawrach, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> armleuten, unsicher sey.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> armleute durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> daran weysen wöllet, daz sie den
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers armman sichern auf
                                <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> reht, als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und
                            <expan>hete<ex>n</ex></expan> sie <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czu
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers <expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> icht
                                <expan>czusprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darümb so wil in der
                                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> von <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> armman
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> slewnigs
                                <expan>reht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen, <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> er des
                        ermant wirdt. <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>.
                        <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
